 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007185652/https://geonames.usgs.gov/apex/f?p=138:3:::NO:3:P3_FID,P3_TITLE:1828629,Hooks%20Point
 |dead-url=no
 }}</ref>，整座島嶼則位在帕羅奧圖海灣帆船碼頭的正東方。

